  Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch   1. Extract the bottleneck features corresponding to the chosen CNN model.
  2. Supply the bottleneck features as input to the model to return the predicted vector. Note that the argmax of this prediction vector gives the index of the predicted dog breed.
  3. Use the dog_names array defined in Step 0 of this notebook to return the corresponding breed.

The functions to extract the bottleneck features can be found in extract_bottleneck_features.py, and they have been imported in an earlier code cell. To obtain the bottleneck features corresponding to your chosen CNN architecture, you need to use the function

extract_{network}

where {network}, in the above filename, should be one of VGG19, Resnet50, InceptionV3, or Xception.

### TODO: Write a function that takes a path to an image as input
### and returns the dog breed that is predicted by the model.
from extract_bottleneck_features import *

def InceptionV3_predict_breed(img_path):
    # extract bottleneck features
    bottleneck_feature = extract_InceptionV3(path_to_tensor(img_path))
    # obtain predicted vector
    predicted_vector = InceptionV3_model.predict(bottleneck_feature)
    # print(predicted_vector)
    # print(np.argsort(predicted_vector[0]))
#   print np.argsort(predicted_vector)
    # return dog breed that is predicted by the model
    return dog_names[np.argmax(predicted_vector)]

def dog_human_predictor(path):
    
    print ("Detecting match for Dog in the Image ...")
    if dog_detector(path):
        print ("Sounds like there is a dog in the picture !!! Lets get the breed ...")
        predicted_breed=InceptionV3_predict_breed(path)
        print('The breed of the dog closely matches to %s' %predicted_breed )
        
    elif face_detector(path):
        print ("Detected Human face in the Supplied Image !!!")
        predicted_breed=InceptionV3_predict_breed(path)
        print('No Offense ! But you and %s have lotta similarities !!' %predicted_breed)

Algorithm performed better on the real world data sets. It awas able to predict random dog breeds that were provided to it from the internet. It was not able to predict the breed of pug as there was no training data associated with it. But the breed it predicted, which is "Bulldog" , is closely resembling the Pug. So, the algorithm predicts the breed of the dog pretty well. The improvement points that I can think of:

  1. We can find the features that the model is relying on to find the dog breed. Mostly we can identify the wrongly predicted ones from test set and train the model to predict that. For ex. Icelandic Sheepdog and German Shepheard.

  2. More training needed in detecting the dog breed that human resembles. It would be interesting to note which significant features that the model is relying on to come up with breed.

  3. It would be interesting to try out different layers with various filters modfiying the transfer learning that was used. But obviously it needs more processing power in the system if we were to replicate the entire layer. But it can improve the accuracy of detection.

  4. Plot the learning curve to check if the model improves with more data and if so, collect more images for the wrongly predicted ones for the model to learn, train and make better prediction.
